{"item_id":"181d2555f2:0","text":"PxrBarnLightFilter 允许我们创建物理准确的 window barns（窗形遮扉），以正确的阴影模拟真实片场灯光。它的其他用途包括在大型场景中控制反弹光。除了 physical mode（物理模式）之外，它还提供 analytic mode（解析模式）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:2","text":"Barn Mode"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:3","text":"选择 barn mode：physical (0) barn 的行为类似一扇打开的窗口，灯光从中落下。falloff 和 blur 由灯光尺寸、到灯光的距离以及与 barn 的距离决定。analytic (1) barn 具有固定投影和手动 falloff 控制。可能时请使用 Physical Barn。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:4","text":"Projection (For Analytic Barn Only)"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:5","text":"Directional"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:6","text":"当开启此项时，纹理会使用正交投影沿某个方向投射。关闭时，纹理会使用由 Apex 指定的焦点进行投射。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:7","text":"Shear X"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:8","text":"沿 X-axis 对投影进行剪切。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:9","text":"Shear Y"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:10","text":"沿 Y-axis 对投影进行剪切。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:11","text":"Apex"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:12","text":"barn 中心与投影中心之间的距离。仅当 Directional 关闭时适用。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:13","text":"Use Light Direction"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:14","text":"如果开启此项，投影方向由光源中心的位置决定。否则，它只会跟随 cookie 的方向。WARNING：这不适用于 dome 和 mesh lights。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:15","text":"Barn Shape"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:16","text":"Width"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:17","text":"barn 内部区域的宽度（X-axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:18","text":"Height"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:19","text":"barn 内部区域的高度（Y-axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:20","text":"Radius"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:21","text":"内部 barn 方形角部的半径。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:22","text":"Edge"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:23","text":"边缘区域的厚度。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:24","text":"Pre Barn"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:25","text":"灯光到达 barn 之前受到的效果。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:26","text":"no effect (0)"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:27","text":"cone (1)"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:28","text":"no light (2)"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:29","text":"Scale"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:30","text":"Scale Width"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:31","text":"缩放内部 barn 形状的宽度（X axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:32","text":"Scale Height"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:33","text":"缩放内部 barn 形状的高度（Y axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:34","text":"Refine Edges"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:35","text":"Left"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:36","text":"左侧区域的额外尺寸（-X axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:37","text":"Right"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:38","text":"右侧区域的额外尺寸（+X axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:39","text":"Bottom"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:40","text":"底部区域的额外尺寸（-Y axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:41","text":"Top"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:42","text":"顶部区域的额外尺寸（+Y axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:43","text":"Scale Edges"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:44","text":"Left Edge"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:45","text":"左侧区域的额外柔化尺寸（-X axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:46","text":"Right Edge"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:47","text":"右侧区域的额外柔化尺寸（+X axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:48","text":"Bottom Edge"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:49","text":"底部区域的额外柔化尺寸（-Y axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:50","text":"Top Edge"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:51","text":"顶部区域的额外柔化尺寸（+Y axis）。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:52","text":"Multiplier"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:54","text":"控制此 light filter 的强度。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:55","text":"Invert"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:56","text":"指定在应用此 light filter 之前，是否反转其结果。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:57","text":"Intensity"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:58","text":"下方 diffuse 和 specular 贡献的全局 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:59","text":"Diffuse"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:60","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 diffuse contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:61","text":"Specular"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:62","text":"此 light filter 结果用于 specular contribution 的 multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:63","text":"Density Falloff (For Analytic Barn Only)"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:64","text":"Density Near"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:65","text":"从 barn 起算，密度插值开始的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:66","text":"Density Far"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:67","text":"从 barn 起算，密度插值结束的位置距离。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:68","text":"Density Near Val"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:69","text":"模糊插值开始处的 Density multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:70","text":"Density Far Val"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:71","text":"模糊插值结束处的 Density multiplier。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:72","text":"Density Exponent"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:73","text":"密度插值的 exponent。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:75","text":"Combine Mode"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:76","text":"mult"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:77","text":": 所有滤镜的结果会相乘。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:78","text":"max"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:79","text":": 使用所有滤镜中的最大结果。这最适合灰度灯光滤镜。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:80","text":"min"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:81","text":": 使用所有滤镜中的最小结果。这最适合灰度灯光滤镜。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:82","text":"screen"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:83","text":": 类似于 max 操作，但会以更平滑的方式组合渐变。这最适合灰度灯光。"}
{"item_id":"181d2555f2:84","text":"附加在灯光上的 Light filters 会按各自的 combined mode（组合模式）分组。同一组中的 Light filters 会一起执行，并按 combined mode 进行组合。各组按以下顺序执行（max、min、screen，然后 mult），并且会相互相乘；这意味着 mult 组中把结果变黑的 filter 会将所有其他 filter 清零。"}
{"id": "e68b36b17cbd990802f57741cb75cf3a73fa66a61999b0cd70e3cf7d26cfb25f", "item_id": "181d2555f2:1", "text": "Parameters（参数）"}
{"id": "77a283d69258c2ae985dc2343725d0af253da0fc1d87626966f7cefe4a3c7469", "item_id": "181d2555f2:53", "text": "Density"}
{"id": "f1d391844bc65573f53c0c894750b2c4c7b5a63f81897dc2d03474e6c877f728", "item_id": "181d2555f2:74", "text": "Combine Mode"}
